这里处理的全部是单链表:

```c
typedef struct node {
	char *data; 
	struct node *next; 
} node_t;
```

我们约定一个打印链表的函数:

```c
void list_display(node_t *head)
{
	for (; head; head = head->next)
		printf("%s ", head->data);
	printf("\n");
}
```

